                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7541" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-1888</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2123 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">海信整合三电：生死时刻的背水一战（上）（下）</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Hisense Integrated Sanden: Fight to life or death  (Part one) (Part two)</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">刘素，张晓莹，杨宏力，梁树广</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">山东财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">海信集团</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">家电行业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">跨国并购；整合；并购动因；策略选择；2023百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">International acquisition；Integration；Acquisition motives；Posssible Solution strategies</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">三电控股株式会社（以下简称三电）是全球领先的汽车空调压缩机和汽车空调系统一级制造供应商，其开发的新一代电动压缩机、综合热管理系统和汽车空调产品在新能源汽车领域已经得到大量应用。近年来，受外部环境的冲击以及自身经营不善等问题的影响，该公司的经营陷入困境，濒临破产。2021年5月31日，海信家电出资13.02亿人民币，成为三电的控股股东，持有其约75%的表决权。海信刚接手之际，恰逢全球汽车厂商5年规划周期的起始，三电面临签单的机会窗口期。如果三电没能在这一轮竞争中赢回客户的订单，它未来在很长时间内将无法扭转亏损困局。作为一个并不精通汽车行业运营规律和商业逻辑的“外行东家”，面对“躺平”的三电，海信陷入了一个内外交困、进退两难的决策窘境。要想在短期内推出契合行业发展趋势和市场需求的新一代产品，恢复客户的信心，改善公司的财务状况，海信该如何谋划破局之道？海信收购东芝电视、欧洲的Gorenje集团后，助力他们快速实现扭亏为盈的成功经验，是否可以直接移植到整合三电的过程中？海信能否快速接受、学习和适应新行业的游戏规则？过去风光无限的三电能否在海信的带领下，重整旗鼓，否极泰来？在这个生死攸关的抉择时刻，一场惊心动魄的背水之战正在上演。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Sanden Holdings Corporation (hereinafter referred to as Sanden) is a leading global supplier of automotive air conditioning compressors and automotive air conditioning systems. Its new generation electric compressors, comprehensive thermal management systems, and automotive air conditioning products have been widely used in the field of new energy vehicles. In recent years, due to the impact of external environment and issues such as poor management, the company&#39;s operations have fallen into difficulties and are on the brink of bankruptcy. On May 31, 2021, Hisense Home Appliances Group Co., Ltd. invested 1.302 billion RMB to become the controlling shareholder of Sanden, holding approximately 75% of its voting rights. When Hisense just took over, it coincided with the beginning of the five-year planning cycle of the global automobile manufacturers, and Sanden faced a window of opportunity for signing orders. If Sanden fails to win back customer orders in this round of competition, it will not be able to reverse its loss situation for a long time in the future. As a &quot;layman&quot; who is not proficient in the operational laws and business logic of the automotive industry, Hisense has faced a dilemma of internal and external difficulties and decision-making in the face of &quot;lying flat&quot; Sanden. To launch a new generation of products that align with industry development trends and market demand in the short term, restore customer confidence, and improve the company&#39;s financial situation, how should Hisense plan a way to break the situation? Can the successful experience of Hisense&#39;s acquisition of Toshiba Television and Gorenje Group in Europe, which helped them quickly turn losses into profits, be directly transplanted into the process of integrating Sanden? Can Hisense quickly accept, learn and adapt to the game rules of the new industry? Can Sanden, which used to have unlimited scenery, under the leadership of Hisense, regroup and turn the tide? At this critical moment of life or death, a thrilling battle is unfolding.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》、《跨国经营与管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国企业跨国并购的动因；逆向并购中的整合困境；并购后的效果；整合过程面临的风险及有效应对措施等</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-09</td>
                            </tr>
